{"type":"section","nativeType":"section","number":"6226","heading":"Annual report and certification on status of security of atomic energy defense facilities1So in original. Probably should be “Biennial”.1","label":"6226 Annual report and certification on status of security of atomic energy defense facilities1So in original. Probably should be “Biennial”.1","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6226","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/stA/ptVI/sptB/ch605/schI","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs6226","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":["Editorial Notes","Prior ProvisionsProvisions similar to those in this section were contained in , War and National Defense, prior to repeal by .section 2657 of Title 50Pub. L. 119–60, § 3111(b)(1)","Amendments2025—, realigned margins.Pub. L. 119–60, § 3111(d)(2)(B)"],"amendments":["Amendments2025—, realigned margins.Pub. L. 119–60, § 3111(d)(2)(B)"],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"a","heading":".—Report and Certification on Nuclear Security Enterprise","label":"a .—Report and Certification on Nuclear Security Enterprise","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6226/a","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6226","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs6226%2Fa","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6226/a/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6226/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs6226%2Fa%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6226/a/1/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6226/a/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs6226%2Fa%2F1%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"a report detailing the status of security at facilities holding Category I and II quantities of special nuclear material that are administered by the Administration; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6226/a/1/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6226/a/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs6226%2Fa%2F1%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"written certification that such facilities are secure and that the security measures at such facilities meet the security standards and requirements of the Administration and the Department of Energy.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6226/a/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6226/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs6226%2Fa%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6226/a/2/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6226/a/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs6226%2Fa%2F2%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the deficiency that resulted in the Administrator being unable to make the certification;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6226/a/2/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6226/a/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs6226%2Fa%2F2%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the actions to be taken to correct the deficiency; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"C","heading":null,"label":"C","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6226/a/2/C","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6226/a/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs6226%2Fa%2F2%2FC","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"timelines for taking such actions.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"3","heading":null,"label":"3","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6226/a/3","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6226/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs6226%2Fa%2F3","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"Not later than December 1 of each even-numbered year, the Secretary shall submit to the congressional defense committees the unaltered report, certification, and any corrective action plans submitted by the Administrator under paragraphs (1) and (2) together with any comments of the Secretary.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"b","heading":".—Report and Certification on Atomic Energy Defense Facilities Not Administered by the Administration","label":"b .—Report and Certification on Atomic Energy Defense Facilities Not Administered by the Administration","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6226/b","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6226","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs6226%2Fb","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6226/b/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6226/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs6226%2Fb%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effec